 n\u00e6rheten av fulle folk, derfor arrangerer vi i Nabla linjeforening ogs\u00e5 alkoholfrie kvelder. Det vi h\u00f8rer er at flere f\u00f8ler seg mer inkludert og f\u00e5r lyst til \u00e5 v\u00e6re med p\u00e5 det linjeforeninga arrangerer, sier Uri Hageberg."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "d1ccaa83db6b2a9d5f65f72145ef24bc1b54c5af0ae9e02e03925da910713072"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-04-12T20:23:02.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Urovekkende mange studenter har farlige drikkevaner. Tirsdag l\u00e6rte studentfadderne hvordan de skal finne sin lykkepromille."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/trondheim/article12592016.ece/obddzj/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Studenter"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d4c52b9d5ad31222777af745b4f4abaf29d3143a.jpg?59884481"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Studentene skal finne den \u00abperfekte promillen\u00bb -adressa.no", "Farlige drikkevaner", "F\u00f8ler p\u00e5 fadder-ansvaret", "Tar grep"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "d4c52b9d5ad31222777af745b4f4abaf29d3143a"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Studenter", "Studentsamskipnaden", "alkohol", "Rus", "Helsedirektoratet"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Studenter,Studentsamskipnaden,alkohol,Rus,Helsedirektoratet"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["pareto", "handelsh\u00f8yskolen bi"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["studenter", "perfekte promillen"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["larsen gjerdalen", "helsedirektoratet", "velferdstinget", "studentsamskipnaden", "oslo og andreas larsen gjerdalen", "studentenes", "ur